<div class="RtCol" style="margin-top: 65px;"> <span style="font: 1.875em/120% georgia, 'Century Schoolbook L', serif; letter-spacing: 0.02em;" itemprop="alternativeHeadline">Set aside <BR>what you know about equipment for a minute, <BR>and focus on the actual physics.</span></div>

